This website uses Python and Flask to do the following:
● Simulate a user login
● Redirect the user to a Dashboard page
This website incorporates a basic user functionality of logins, logouts, and authentications. 

To run this application.
1. Check all the requirements in requirements.txt file are met.
2. Download the 'Flask_Python_WebProject'
3. Open the project in Python IDE (eg. Pycharm)
4. update following config information in '__init__' file (line number 22,23,24) according to your installed MySQL server host, user and password
        app.config['MYSQL_HOST'] = 'localhost'
        app.config['MYSQL_USER'] = 'root'
        app.config['MYSQL_PASSWORD'] = 'Password'
5. Run '__init__' file.
